Workflow.Name: HELPER - Remove User from Security Role
Workflow.Description: Removes a user from a SR in a given envt Tailored to our Envt SR Identities work. As such it takes in User as Display Name, Business Unit as Display Name, and SR as either Display Name or TID if it has one.
